            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37687670">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">咖啡冲泡被称为“萃取”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-05-01 17:54</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                咖啡冲泡被称为“萃取”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37687670/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
